---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="mx-16 pb-8">
    <header class="my-8">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-center text-primary/40">
        PRODUCTS
      </h1>

      <p class="text-base text-center font-stretch-expanded">
        Designed with Passion. Built for Your Desk.
      </p>

      <p class="text-center text-xs text-primary/40 leading-4">Read more</p>
    </header>

    <p class="my-2">
      At SmartDesk Robotics, we believe your workspace should be more than just
      functional — it should be inspiring. That’s why we craft intelligent,
      customizable, and beautifully designed robots that don’t just sit on your
      desk — they work with you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl my-4">🤖 Edison – Your Desktop Companion</h2>

    <img src="/images/camera1.jpg" class="w-1/2 my-2" />

    <p class="my-2">
      Meet Edison, the ultimate personal assistant for your desk. Whether you’re
      a developer, creative, student, or productivity nerd — Edison is here to
      keep you focused, organized, and even entertained.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl my-4">What can Edison do?</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>🎙️ Recognize your voice and face</li>
      <li>📅 Manage your schedule and reminders</li>
      <li>💬 Answer your questions in real time</li>
      <li>📊 Display personal data like finances, habits, or tasks</li>
      <li>🖥️ Connect to a second screen for rich visual output</li>
      <li>🎨 Fully customizable appearance and personality</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="my-2">
      With Edison, your workspace becomes smarter, more personal, and a lot more
      fun.
    </p>

    <h3 class="my-2">🎛️ Add-On Modules (Coming Soon!)</h3>

    <img src="/images/board1.jpg" class="w-1/2 my-2" />

    <p class="my-2">
      We’re constantly developing new modules and integrations so you can expand
      your Edison’s capabilities. Think:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Smart light control</li>
      <li>Voice-controlled music playback</li>
      <li>Health habit tracking</li>
      <li>Smart notifications</li>
      <li>App integrations (Notion, Google Calendar, GitHub…)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl my-4">⚙️ Built with Creativity & Care</h2>

    <img src="/images/board2.jpg" alt="" class="w-1/2 my-2" />

    <p class="my-2">
      Every unit we create reflects our passion for innovative design,
      human-friendly tech, and seamless integration. From 3D-printed cases to
      tailored software features — each Edison is a small piece of robotics
      magic made just for your desk.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl my-4">✨ Why a Desk Robot?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Because your workspace should work for you.</li>
      <li>Because tech should feel alive.</li>
      <li>Because productivity doesn’t have to be boring.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="my-2">Ready to bring Edison to your desk?</p>
    <p class="my-2">Stay tuned — pre-orders are opening soon.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
